{"tid":175437,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"文學賞識：朱自清《背影》","createTime":"2017-03-27T13:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T09:27:26.000Z","uid":34394,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"edea2878e1e73658a00c2f4969e4abf9efe43f75","tid":175437,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:17:02.000Z","msg":"朱自清寫下背影一文，除了單純表達對父親的愛，還有修補與父親關係的意味。文初寫道「我與父親不相見已有二年餘了」，實是透露出父子關係的疏離。據説朱自清父親朱小坡與其媳婦武忠謙有嫌隙，而且父親更曾經私自偷取朱自清教學的薪資，此事使他們的關係越來越惡劣，最終導致朱自清憤而離開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/loh0r5k8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Floh0r5k8&h=188fe83b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲楊岳橋<br />\n<br />\n據說，當朱小坡看到他兒子寫下如此感動人心的篇章，當下便立刻熱淚盈眶，隨手拿起紙筆，就寫下給兒子的信。<br />\n信中道：「Ching Ho Ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n～完～"},{"pid":"049466cda1a1b417bbfa1461c2b606a56bb7d299","tid":175437,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:19:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9be2ba0938028a128e58977b7f81acf227a16eaa","tid":175437,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:21:41.000Z","msg":"偷偷留下負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04ae5daa60a246676a33dccc1d10c4c62232968","tid":175437,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"162225aabf09e0a51af149b56947286ef160ba2e","tid":175437,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:22:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72a798ede0d1d697cccb020d44bba982e3b54209","tid":175437,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:23:10.000Z","msg":"大家一起了解多一點文學作品背後深層意義"},{"pid":"4c1fd6fbe354975f6721a205792edd8a0a10dc4d","tid":175437,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:25:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f481d5eb958b2d409a37d3d55bd6dd7dd11215","tid":175437,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:26:43.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"145057897098edbe00e51a91965eb859d5bb67f0","tid":175437,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ac6ac007afd4464af92edbd8880ba52e017991","tid":175437,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c99fd51d1684bde7db4ad5056bcd5b375b5edef","tid":175437,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785a8cb7d50f3e43ab77e42ea74f1cefd7bd0e26","tid":175437,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T22:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b95a74239d7351b2f43ee6b99c9186fa60a9124","tid":175437,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abdd958dd3bd2711bc5849f112f3e6f6d88a5fc2","tid":175437,"uid":87563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:04:15.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"f601af323be8c73797149df1da216a677da7c42c","tid":175437,"uid":64609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:33:52.000Z","msg":"From 隔離POST<br />\n<br />\n我說道，「爸爸，你走吧。」他往車外看了看，說，「我買幾個橘子去。你就在此地，不要走動。」我看那邊月台的柵欄外有幾個賣東西的等著顧客。走到那邊月台，須穿過鐵道，須跳下去又爬上去。父親是一個胖子，走過去自然要費事些。我本來要去的，他不肯，只好讓他去。我看見他戴著黑布小帽，穿著黑布大馬褂，深青布棉袍，蹣跚地走到鐵道邊，慢慢探身下去，尚不大難。可是他穿過鐵道，要爬上那邊月台，就不容易了。他用兩手攀著上面，兩腳再向上縮；他肥胖的身子向左微傾，顯出努力的樣子。這時我看見他的背影，我的淚很快地流下來了。我趕緊拭乾了淚，怕他看見，也怕別人看見。突然一班高鐵列車進站，他試圖搶在列車前，但不成功。結果被夾在列車1號車廂與月台之間，列車立即停車。他只有上半身露出在月台之上，表現得相當痛苦。事發後車站工作人員即報警求助，警方和消防其後到場救援，利用破拆機械救出父親，但在場救護人員其後宣布父親傷重死亡。事件亦導致列車服務暫停一個多小時。"},{"pid":"ba2d13e4db08efdf8b6c2e45db2aabbfe10cc614","tid":175437,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T09:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}